   NEW YORK -- Citizens &amp; Southern Corp. and Sovran Financial
Corp., which are merging, are being deleted from the southern
regional banks industry group of the Dow Jones Equity Market
Index, effective today. The merged concern, C&amp;S/Sovran Corp.,
is being added to the group.
