   Royale Belge S.A.
</HL>
<DATE>
09/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   B.ROB
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
INSURANCE (INS)
FULL LINE INSURANCE (INF)
</IN>
<LP>
   BRUSSELS -- Royale Belge S.A., a Belgian insurer, said it
acquired the Belgian insurance operations of Groupe Le Foyer
of Luxembourg. Terms weren't disclosed.
   The operations have annual premium income of more than 2
billion Belgian francs ($63 million), mostly in automotive,
property and, to a lesser extent, life insurance, Royale
Belge said.
</LP>
